{"tid":991803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港明天更好基金執委會主席陳啟宗：我唔睇香港新聞","createTime":"2019-01-22T16:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T16:11:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"29390c99e2596c75aa953be7bf295f776434dab4","tid":991803,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:01:43.000Z","msg":"香港明天更好基金執委會主席、恒隆地產董事長陳啟宗今午與傳媒茶敘時表示，對中美貿易戰不會過分悲觀，認為有解決可能性，問題在於美國總統特朗普何時有內部政治需要。不過他指擔心香港，憂慮美國會因政治原因拿香港來「祭旗」，故其基金會主要向外部解釋香港事情。<br />\n<br />\n對於律政司決定就UGL事件不檢控前特首梁振英，以及梁會否「回朝」做特首，陳啟宗稱自己不看香港新聞，形容是「茶杯裏的風波」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190122/s00001/1548147034903/【貿易戰】陳啟宗指不過分悲觀-料中國會讓步-惟憂美國拿香港「祭旗」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190122%2Fs00001%2F1548147034903%2F%E3%80%90%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E3%80%91%E9%99%B3%E5%95%9F%E5%AE%97%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%8E%E5%88%86%E6%82%B2%E8%A7%80-%E6%96%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%AE%93%E6%AD%A5-%E6%83%9F%E6%86%82%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%8B%BF%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8C%E7%A5%AD%E6%97%97%E3%80%8D&d=u8%2Bqoai3bpL%2Fx%2BgE41AThDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=8926b3a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190122%2Fs00001%2F1548147034903%2F%E3%80%90%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E3%80%91%E9%99%B3%E5%95%9F%E5%AE%97%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%8E%E5%88%86%E6%82%B2%E8%A7%80-%E6%96%99%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%AE%93%E6%AD%A5-%E6%83%9F%E6%86%82%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%8B%BF%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8C%E7%A5%AD%E6%97%97%E3%80%8D&h=5fd3fbac\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190122/s00001/1548147034903/【貿易戰】陳啟宗指不過分悲觀-料中國會讓步-惟憂美國拿香港「祭旗」</a>"},{"pid":"3f68e2a8de642f94808423f96e3fd66c4c8a850f","tid":991803,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T16:11:03.000Z","msg":"駝鳥"}]}